Package Dependencies
--------------------
- libmysqlpp (available via apt)
- libpthread (available via apt)
- libdl (should already be installed on ubuntu)
- libmysqlclient (available via apt)

Install
-------
Binary will be installed in the `pwd` of the package.

./configure
make install

Module Install
--------------
Loadable modules will be installed in the package `pwd`/lib/

cd modules
make install
cd ..

Running
-------
./opentest -c etc/opentest.conf

Shutdown
--------
Type /QUIT in the console
